Max time step, energy fluctuations and energy drift for different values of temperature and number of particles (actually,the n. of particles is 4 N^3, crystal structure)
criterio per max dt: esplode prima di t=100

T=0.722
N=1 dt=0.004-0.005
dt=0.004 drift=(-1.9,163dt), (2.9, 1982dt), i.e. about 5/100
dt=0.002 drift=(-1.6,194dt), (-0.52,5996dt), i.e. about 0.4/100
dt=0.001 mean=-1.6, std=0.09

N=2 dt=0.025-0.03
dt=0.025 drift=(-150,0), (-145,400), i.e. about 5/400
dt=0.01 drift=(-149.3,0), (-148.6,200), i.e. about 0.7/200
dt=0.005 mean=-149.4, std=0.09

N=3 dt=0.025-0.03
dt=0.025 drift=(-556.5,0), (-555.5,1000), i.e. about 1/1000
dt=0.01 drift=(-556.6,0), (-556.7,400), i.e. about -0.1/400 -- mean=-149.1, std=0.09
dt=0.005 mean=-556.6, std=0.02

N=4 dt=0.03-0.035
dt=0.03 drift=(-1310,0), (-1290,100), i.e. about 20/100
dt=0.025 drift=(-1308.5,0),(-1307,200) i.e. about 1.5/200
dt=0.015 drift=(-1308.8,0),(-1308.3,140) i.e. about 0.5/140
dt=0.01 drift=(-1308.7,0),(-1308.6,100) i.e. about 0.1/100 -- mean=-1308.7, std=0.06
dt=0.005 mean=-1308.8, std=0.02

N=5 dt=0.03-0.035
dt=0.03 drift=(-2590,0),(-2540,300) i.e. about 50/300
dt=0.015 drift=(-2595,0),(-2594.6,140) i.e. about 0.4/140
dt=0.01 drift=(-2595,0),(-2594.6,100) i.e. about 0.4/100 -- mean=-2594.7, std=0.11
dt=0.005 mean=-2595.0, std=0.02

N=10 dt=0.03-0.035
dt=0.03 drift=(-21010,0),(-20960,50) i.e. about 50/50
dt=0.01 drift=(-21024,0),(-21023,100) i.e. about 1/100
dt=0.003 mean=-21024.7, std=0.06

