T=0.1
N=1 dt=0.01-0.015
dt=0.01 drift=(-5,0),(-3.6,100) i.e. about 1.4/100 (exponential)
dt=0.005 mean=-5.1, std=0.11

N=2 dt=0.05-0.055
dt=0.05 drift=(-182.5,0),(-178,100) i.e. about 4.5/100
